    "en": {
      "title": "The girl who attacked the MP and pushed him into the Beira lake was arrested",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A 26-year-old girl was arrested for assaulting a local councilor and pushing him into the Beira lake, the police press office said.",
        "This incident happened on May 9. It is stated in the complaint he submitted to the Colombo Crimes Division that he stole the wallet of money and pushed it into the Beira lake.",
        "The young woman was arrested after coming to the Colombo Crimes Division to give a statement."
      ],
